WF-005 | Upload completed import file | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Upload | on_success: starts import and adds entry to import history
WF-006 | Download import result from import history | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Download | on_success: downloads import result file
WF-007 | Submit Create Client wizard (linear multi-step) | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Submit | on_success: creates client in Pending status
WF-008 | Pending: Activate client | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Pending | terminal: Activate | on_success: activates client and changes status to Active
WF-009 | Pending: Edit client | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Pending | terminal: Edit | on_success: opens edit client form
WF-010 | Pending: Reject client | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Pending | terminal: Reject | on_success: marks client as Rejected
WF-011 | Pending: Withdraw client | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Pending | terminal: Withdraw | on_success: marks client as Withdrawn
WF-012 | Active: Edit client | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Active | terminal: Edit | on_success: opens edit client form
WF-013 | Active: Transfer client to another office | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Active | terminal: Transfer Client | on_success: transfers client to selected destination office
WF-014 | Active: Close client | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Active | terminal: Close | on_success: closes client and changes status to Closed
WF-015 | Active: Add charge to client | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Active | terminal: Add Charge | on_success: adds a charge entry to the client
WF-016 | Active: Initiate new loan for client | actor: <role> | branch: entity_state == Active | terminal: New Loan | on_success: initiates new loan creation for the client
